videos.description: Trying to convert on fourth-and-2, Feleipe Franks over throws the pass to Lamical Perine to turn the ball over to Florida State.
videos.headline: Florida fails on 4th down

videos.description: Feleipe Franks is sacked by Florida State's Brian Burns, who forces the fumble and Jacob Pugh takes it all the way for a Seminoles' touchdown.
videos.headline: Burns' sack, fumble leads to Florida State TD

videos.description: Florida State receiver Auden Tate has the ball bounce off of his foot and up in the air, where Florida's Duke Dawson grabs it for the interception.
videos.headline: Lucky bounce leads to Florida INT

videos.description: Mark Thompson finds a gap and easily runs into the end zone untouched for a 10-yard touchdown for the Gators.
videos.headline: Florida's Thompson walks into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Feleipe Franks' pass is intended for Brandon Powell, but the ball ricochets off the helmet of a Florida State defender and into the hands of Levonta Taylor for the interception.
videos.headline: Florida pass caroms of defenders helmet for turnover

videos.description: James Blackman connects with an open Nyqwan Murray for a 21-yard touchdown to give the Seminoles the lead over the Gators.
videos.headline: Florida State's Blackman finds Murray for TD

videos.description: Feleipe Franks' pass is intercepted by the Seminoles' Levonta Taylor, who takes it all the way home for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida State's Taylor gets pick-six

videos.description: Feleipe Franks finds Brandon Powell at the back of the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown to chip away at the Seminoles' lead before the half.
videos.headline: Florida gets TD before halftime

videos.description: Florida State head coach Jimbo Fisher breaks down how his team needs to improve on the running game and regroup for the second half.
videos.headline: Fisher: 'We just have to get consistent'

videos.description: Florida head coach Randy Shannon lays out how his team has to keep the momentum rolling and fight its way in the second half.
videos.headline: Shannon: 'We can't have any more turnovers'

videos.description: Cam Akers finds a gap in the defense and rushes into the end zone for a 10-yard touchdown to widen the Seminoles' lead.
videos.headline: Florida State pads lead with TD

videos.description: Feleipe Franks' pass is intercepted by Matthew Thomas, who has a clear path to the end zone but showboats and falls at the 1-yard line. To make matters worse, Thomas is also given a 15-yard unsportsmanlike conduct penalty.
videos.headline: Thomas' showboating costs Florida State defensive TD

videos.description: James Blackman connects with Auden Tate who makes a leaping catch for the Seminoles touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida State's Tate makes impressive TD catch

videos.description: With less than a minute to go in the fourth quarter, Feleipe Franks connects with Brandon Powell for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida's Powell gets second TD of game

videos.description: Seminoles head coach Jimbo Fisher shares his excitement for the team's 38-22 victory over the Gators and explains why the future of the program is so bright.
videos.headline: Fisher jubilant over win against Florida

videos.description: Seminoles pass around an alligator head and cheer after their 38-22 win over the Gators.
videos.headline: Florida State celebrates victory with an alligator head

videos.description: Anthony Becht and Beth Mowins discuss the keys to the Florida State's 38-22 victory over rival Florida and how important their next game is for bowl eligibility.
videos.headline: Becht and Mowins break down Seminoles' win over Gators

videos.description: Florida State scores two defensive touchdowns in a 38-22 win over Florida.
videos.headline: Florida State takes down Florida
